item.title: USS
item.description: I don’t like how these “Uni” are portrayed. They’re too familiar to me. USS is about robot bugs in space that like to archive everything! They live very different from humans. Would they get along, or would another cataclysmic event happen? Last update: 2024/02/17. Generation started 2024/02/14. Releases 0.0.X - “Prologue” HTML
